   <text>
      <body>
         <div type="translation">
            <ab>Has brought Pleein, son of Eudaimon, to the bank of the river, one basket (sargane)  of combustible chaff, for the village of Karanis, for the 13th and 1st year. We, Heron and Kalandos, have signed. (2nd hand) I, Neilos, have signed.</ab>
